{"tid":839602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國男子在非洲公園隨地便溺 被喝止要自行清理","createTime":"2018-09-28T05:21:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T05:54:28.000Z","uid":41404,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ea4dda315f05dbeb8f047249ea445fa6d2424b1a","tid":839602,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T05:21:28.000Z","msg":"中國人愛隨地便溺，成為了國際大笑話。日前，一段中國男子在西非國家加納一個公園內隨地便溺的短片在網絡瘋傳。事件引起外國網民熱議，有外媒批評，中國人無法無天，公然無視迦納的法律。<br />\n<br />\n最近，一名中國人在西非國家迦納的一個公園裏，靠着一棵樹在大便，當地民眾發現後，圍起來斥責他，又要求他用鏟子將自己的糞便收拾乾淨。當地人問這名中國大叔，是不是也會在自己的國家隨地便溺，這名中國人只是不斷道歉，不願正面回應。事件被當地的目擊者拍攝下來，並上傳至社交媒體Instagram分享。<br />\n<br />\n在過去幾年內，大量中國人湧入迦納，他們在當地無法無天，甚至公然無視迦納的法律，當局有必要正視此問題。而不少外國網民睇完片之後都紛紛留言，怒斥該男子的行為。<br />\n<br />\n網民：「可憐的傢伙」、「你知道廁所在哪裏嗎？」、「中國人好像都這樣」、「逮捕他！」、「這非常糟糕」、「不應該用鏟子，應該用雙手清他的糞便」、「自找麻煩的傢伙」、「替他感到難過」。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/chi/1328313/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fchi%2F1328313%2F&d=pcw7TIdDTT%2FzdYOADSDNskbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=5303fe70\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fchi%2F1328313%2F&h=d377d431\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/chi/1328313/</a>"},{"pid":"021ffd77483081cc34a0e067f5d394f25c5d5ba7","tid":839602,"uid":179810,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T05:33:10.000Z","msg":"叻架都有文化過啲五千年文化大國"},{"pid":"442a3986e90d2fa421bef96eb29efd566cd1f433","tid":839602,"uid":44083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T05:38:06.000Z","msg":"片<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7db51e3768f6e4d36d507e9edffd81f4daceba9","tid":839602,"uid":44083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"442a3986e90d2fa421bef96eb29efd566cd1f433","tid":839602,"uid":44083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T05:38:06.000Z","msg":"片<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T05:38:53.000Z","msg":"自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4122f3c3283903bdb3e3d44b5842f49f1fb7baa4","tid":839602,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T05:40:46.000Z","msg":"迦納人<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ce457070e5f57ea0b3a5218a44572453ddef038","tid":839602,"uid":28279,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T05:47:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 文明古國支那人仲廢過非洲人"},{"pid":"70c95f0dfeddb17202002466bfe0a019fd30959a","tid":839602,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T05:54:28.000Z","msg":"使乜俾把鏟佢，叫佢用自己隻腳挖個窿算啦"}]}